    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入 BAPBAP, 这是一款玩家对战的类 Rogue, 没有两场比赛是相同的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邀请到七位好友一起进行全场大乱斗。每轮比赛后随机选择一种特殊能力，尽可能打造出最荒诞（或最令人遗憾）的装备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BAPBAP最好玩的时刻是与能承受背叛的朋友一起玩。使用疯狂的规则创造你自定的游戏，或进入社区运营的服务器，尽情享受混乱。没有匹配。没有等级。只有纯粹、愚蠢的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使用你疯狂的风格打败对方</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >紧凑、自由的战斗会让你尖叫妈妈快拿摄像机。一切攻击和能力都可以躲避，所以如果你被击败，那是你自己的事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/da2562ccd122dcdbbd1580d828b57bac.poster.avif?t=1759970780\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/da2562ccd122dcdbbd1580d828b57bac.webm?t=1759970780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/da2562ccd122dcdbbd1580d828b57bac.mp4?t=1759970780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你可以选择玩一只鸭子</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或者一条金鱼在驾驶机甲。或是俄罗斯武士。或者是有腿的拉面。每个角色都有自己独特的技能组合，每个人都有适合自己的角色设计--即使是怪胎也不例外 👁️👄👁️。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/c4e16b26189030351884e535a7e43777.poster.avif?t=1759970780\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/c4e16b26189030351884e535a7e43777.webm?t=1759970780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/c4e16b26189030351884e535a7e43777.mp4?t=1759970780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随心所欲</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是变身金属巨鸭，还是选择升级炮台能力，抑或是使用毒药，每款游戏都会为您提供全新的随机组合能力。打造协同效应，获得胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/2fb0bdc9800eb97df3ebdfdd4fd84672.poster.avif?t=1759970780\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/2fb0bdc9800eb97df3ebdfdd4fd84672.webm?t=1759970780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/2fb0bdc9800eb97df3ebdfdd4fd84672.mp4?t=1759970780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握环境去打败对方</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用起重机的载荷封锁对方的逃生路线，变身自动售货机进行偷袭，或驾驶 1942 年装甲车虎式坦克来个驾车突袭。BAPBAP 是一个 PvP 沙盒，在这里一切都非常奇怪，但也一切都对劲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/df2e4f10e587d738484ff71bf43e7b7b.poster.avif?t=1759970780\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/df2e4f10e587d738484ff71bf43e7b7b.webm?t=1759970780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/df2e4f10e587d738484ff71bf43e7b7b.mp4?t=1759970780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >适应混乱</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除此以外，您还可能被漫游的巨型粘液击杀、钓到核弹或发现 神剑铲 被卡在石头里--适应能力越强，您就越能获胜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/98d55484844c609cdb54523f49f10dfa.poster.avif?t=1759970780\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/98d55484844c609cdb54523f49f10dfa.webm?t=1759970780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/98d55484844c609cdb54523f49f10dfa.mp4?t=1759970780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打出漂亮的玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是扭转局势的 1V3，打出漂亮的多目标击飞，还是眼睁睁地看着队友被自己的陷阱击中，BAPBAP都能帮助您在我们日益压抑的世界中获得甜美的多巴胺。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/32728e859eb5631aeae9ccf9fa757d01.poster.avif?t=1759970780\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/32728e859eb5631aeae9ccf9fa757d01.webm?t=1759970780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226280/extras/32728e859eb5631aeae9ccf9fa757d01.mp4?t=1759970780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到BAPBAP，在这里，我们不用逻辑。</p>",
